article_title: Analysis Examines 2015 Federal Income Tax Receipt for Iowa, Nation
article_text:
Shenandoah, IA (51601)

Today

Cloudy skies this morning followed by thunderstorms during the afternoon. A few storms may be severe. High around 75F. Winds SSE at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 80%..

Tonight

Thunderstorms likely this evening. Then the chance of scattered thunderstorms overnight. A few storms may be severe. Low 61F. Winds SSW at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 80%.

article_metadata.author: Mary Kuhlman -- Iowa News Service

og.description: (Des Moines) -- Some Iowans will be spending the weekend crunching the numbers on their tax returns ahead of Monday's deadline. But do taxpayers realize exactly where their money goes?
